<BLOCK1><TI>FACTUM OF THE APPLICANT FOR LEAVE TO APPEAL COSTS DECISION (Costs Decision of Justice Markus Koehnen dated March 3, 2018) Returnable on a date to be fixed by the Registrar</TI>
<P>April 12, 2018</P>
<P><LINE><BOLD>MORGANTI &amp; CO., P.C.</BOLD></LINE>
<LINE>One Yonge Street, Suite 1506</LINE>
<LINE>Toronto, ON M5E 1E5</LINE>
<LINE>Tel: (647) 344-1900</LINE>
