<BLOCK1><TI>ORDER</TI>
<P>THIS MOTION made by the Applicant, Georges Benarroch, for leave to appeal the costs decision of Justice Markus Koehnen dated March 3, 2018 (&ldquo;Costs Decision&rdquo;), was considered on the 29th day of June, 2018 at Osgoode Hall 130 Queen St. W. Toronto, Ontario.</P>
